Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,儿童色情片\N{\fs12}Child pornography Roey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.22,0:00:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么能让香农和这种人单独相处呢\N{\fs12}how could you leave Shannon alone with this guy?
