Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨\N{\fs12}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.31,0:01:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fs12}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗\N{\fs12}You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.48,0:01:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我头有点昏\N{\fs12}A little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,那你坐下呀\N{\fs12}Why don't you sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我得跟罗伊好好谈谈\N{\fs12}I gotta talk to Roy.
