Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚想打电话给你们问问你们有没有消息呢\N{\fs12}I was actually just gonna call you... see if you heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊  你在做什么\N{\fs12}What're you doing, Roy?
