Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.22,0:02:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在那后面有一个旧物回收箱\N{\fs12}They got a drop-off box in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.71,0:02:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里  罗伊\N{\fs12}Where are you going, Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我欠了别人钱  他们一直在威胁我\N{\fs12}Those guys I owe, they keep threatening me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找不到马尔科姆就来找我的麻烦\N{\fs12}Now that they can't find Malcolm, it's all on my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.96,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跑路了吗\N{\fs12}You leaving town?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他们给我的期限快到了  但是我没有办法还钱\N{\fs12}I'm running outta time here, and I can't find the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那你带我去见他们吧\N{\fs12}Well, I want you to take me to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行  如果我没有带钱过去\N{\fs12}No way. I show up there without that money,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.58,0:02:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- 这些人会打断我的  - 钱我来还  我还\N{\fs12}- those guys are gonna break my... - I'll pay. I'll pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那好吧\N{\fs12}All right.
