Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,她是一名联邦特工  在帮SAFE做事\N{\fs12}She's a Federal Agent that works with SAFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,- 什么是SAEF  - 就是性侵犯重罪执法\N{\fs12}- What's that? - Sexual Assault Felony Enforcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾莉森来这里负责调查坎迪斯·布莱尔的案子\N{\fs12}Alison came to town on the Candace Bleier case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.32,0:05:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,谁\N{\fs12}Who?
