Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.22,0:05:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,就是在马尔科姆·里维斯工作室照片里的女孩\N{\fs12}The girl in the photos found in Malcolm Reeves' studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.53,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经找了坎迪斯一年多了\N{\fs12}I've been trying to find Candace for over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,直到今天  我们掌握的资料还只是几段录像\N{\fs12}Up until today, all that's surfaced is a few videos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.06,0:05:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得香农可能和这个女孩在一块吗\N{\fs12}You think Shannon might be with this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.88,0:06:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果坎迪斯还活着的话  就有可能\N{\fs12}lf Candace is still alive, it's a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.53,0:06:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,法林先生  仅仅因为马尔科姆·里维斯\N{\fs12}Mr. Fallin, just because Malcolm Reeves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.44,0:06:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有坎迪斯的照片\N{\fs12}was in possession of photographs of Candace
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,并不意味着他抓走了她们\N{\fs12}doesn't mean he took them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,也不意味着他有做伤害您的养女的事\N{\fs12}and doesn't mean he's done anything to your foster child.
