Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一会儿在仓库  一会儿在汽车旅馆  一会儿又在家里了\N{\fs12}Operate out of warehouses and motels and homes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有的时候会住几天  有的时候就待几个小时\N{\fs12}Sometimes for days, sometimes just for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你能不能告诉我  还是有可能找到她的\N{\fs12}Well, can you tell me it's not impossible to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们得把他们的作品卖出去\N{\fs12}They do have to sell their product.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这是追踪他们的一个办法\N{\fs12}That's one way to track them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.98,0:06:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,通过他们在互联网或者当地报纸的背面\N{\fs12}Through encrypted codes they post on the Internet
