Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.48,0:28:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得我吗\N{\fs12}Do you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我会帮你找个地方暂时住在那里  好吗\N{\fs12}I'm gonna help to find you a nice place to stay for a while, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.49,0:28:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会有人没有最喜欢的颜色呢\N{\fs12}How come you don't have a favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.91,0:29:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs12}Uh... I... I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.70,0:29:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都有自己最喜欢的颜色啊\N{\fs12}Everyone has a favorite color.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.72,0:29:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,紫色吧\N{\fs12}Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.80,0:29:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs12}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.14,0:29:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,紫色  紫色挺好的\N{\fs12}Violet. Seems like a nice color.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.66,0:29:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,别逗了\N{\fs12}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.70,0:29:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的  听着  - 我要看电影了\N{\fs12}- Honey, listen... - I'm gonna watch television.
