Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.37,0:29:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我去咨询了下  想给你提供一些帮助\N{\fs12}I talked to some people about getting you some help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.31,0:29:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,有位女医生很不错\N{\fs12}There's this one lady who evidently is very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.32,0:29:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她帮助过很多孩子\N{\fs12}She's done a lot of work with kids
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.69,0:29:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,经历过这些的   也就是你经历的这些\N{\fs12}who've... been through what you've been through,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.25,0:29:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以  我让劳瑞请她过来\N{\fs12}and... so l, uh... asked Laurie to... to bring her over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.54,0:29:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,什么时候\N{\fs12}When?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.92,0:29:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,一小时之内\N{\fs12}ln about, uh, about an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.10,0:29:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事  伯顿  我不需要找人聊\N{\fs12}I'm fine, Burton. I don't have to talk to anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.23,0:29:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- 亲爱的  听着  - 我没事  伯顿  好吗\N{\fs12}- Honey, look... - I'm fine, Burton, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.95,0:29:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,香农  事实就是  我自己可能需要帮助\N{\fs12}Shannon... the fact is l, uh... I probably need a little help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.26,0:30:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,随便吧\N{\fs12}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.31,0:30:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好无聊\N{\fs12}I'm bored.
