Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.94,0:30:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你真好\N{\fs12}That's very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.19,0:30:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.78,0:30:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你有电视吗\N{\fs12}You got a TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.35,0:30:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,没有  这里没有\N{\fs12}No, not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.24,0:30:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我是尼克·法林\N{\fs12}Nick Fallin.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.49,0:30:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,劳瑞·绍尔特和一位辅导员今天过来和我们聊了聊\N{\fs12}You know, Laurie Solt came over to talk to us with a... a counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.46,0:30:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.64,0:30:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,香农说她去楼上看电视\N{\fs12}Shannon says she'd be up in her room watching TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.20,0:30:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,她们到了之后我上楼叫她\N{\fs12}They got here, and I go upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.38,0:30:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- 她不在楼上了  - 她走了吗\N{\fs12}- She's not there. - She's gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.49,0:30:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有听到她离开\N{\fs12}I didn't hear her leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.09,0:30:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,- 你报警了吗  - 没有  我没必要报警\N{\fs12}- Did you call the police? - No, I didn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.17,0:31:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,劳瑞·绍尔特很生气\N{\fs12}Laurie Solt-- she was angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.73,0:31:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她跟我说我再也管不住香农了\N{\fs12}Told me she didn't think I could handle Shannon anymore.
