Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.23,0:31:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs12}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.51,0:31:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好  罗伊\N{\fs12}Yeah. Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.04,0:31:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  好的\N{\fs12}Yeah. Okay.
