Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.08,0:31:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊现在陪着香农在马尔科姆的工作室\N{\fs12}Roy's with Shannon at Malcolm's studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.03,0:31:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的  你还好吗\N{\fs12}Honey, you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.47,0:31:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我  我需要你的帮助\N{\fs12}l-- I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.79,0:31:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了  - 我们进去谈吧\N{\fs12}- What's going on? - I need to talk to you inside.
