Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.89,0:31:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我陪着她\N{\fs12}I'll stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.43,0:31:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要坐到车上\N{\fs12}You want to sit in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.77,0:32:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我接到了马尔科姆的电话说香农又到他的工作室了\N{\fs12}So I get this call from Malcolm, and he says that Shannon's back here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.26,0:32:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,他想让她离开  因为她给他添了很多麻烦\N{\fs12}and he... wants her out because of all the trouble she causes him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.48,0:32:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我开车过来的时候  一路上我都在想  是香农给他造成麻烦了吗\N{\fs12}I drive over, the whole time thinking, ''The trouble she caused him?''
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.11,0:32:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我进来之后  让香农到外面等我\N{\fs12}So I come in here. I tell her to wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.30,0:32:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我问他做了些什么\N{\fs12}Asked him what he did it for.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.59,0:32:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,他跟我撒谎\N{\fs12}He just lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.50,0:32:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我问他钱是哪里来的\N{\fs12}I asked him where he got the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.51,0:32:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他撒谎\N{\fs12}He lied.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.75,0:32:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我朝他开了枪\N{\fs12}So I shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.13,0:32:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我开了两枪\N{\fs12}Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.88,0:32:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,他错了太多\N{\fs12}After what he did...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.18,0:33:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伊会怎么样\N{\fs12}What's gonna happen to Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.63,0:33:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道啊  亲爱的\N{\fs12}I don't know, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.69,0:33:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他会不会进监狱\N{\fs12}He's going to jail?
