Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.51,0:33:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他说我们可以搬到纽约  或者洛杉矶或者  巴黎去\N{\fs12}He said we could move somewhere like... New York or Los Angeles... or Paris.
