Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.75,0:33:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直说他很爱我\N{\fs12}He said he loved me... all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.36,0:33:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他一直这样跟我说\N{\fs12}He would say that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.12,0:33:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,但是当我到今天那里的时候  他吼了我\N{\fs12}But then... when I got over there... he yelled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.44,0:33:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,骂我  说我给他惹了很多麻烦\N{\fs12}Called me names. Told me I got him into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.47,0:33:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  这些都是他让我做的呀\N{\fs12}But, he's... he's the one who wanted me to do all that stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.70,0:33:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯\N{\fs12}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.52,0:34:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他拍的那些照片还有汽车旅馆的那些录像\N{\fs12}The pictures he took and the tape at the motel...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.47,0:34:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我都记得的  伯顿\N{\fs12}I remember it, Burton.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.57,0:34:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是\N{\fs12}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.73,0:34:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我全都记得\N{\fs12}I remember all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.84,0:34:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我答应过马尔科姆我不会告诉别人\N{\fs12}I just promised Malcolm I'd never tell.
