Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.48,0:34:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs12}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.25,0:34:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好了吗\N{\fs12}You ready?
