Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.04,0:34:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\fs12}That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.60,0:34:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要我帮忙的话就给我打电话  好吗\N{\fs12}lf you need anything... anything at all, you just call me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.25,0:34:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.44,0:35:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这是送你的新家的礼物\N{\fs12}It's for your new house.
