Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.02,0:35:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你把房子买下了吗\N{\fs12}You bought the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.14,0:35:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是付了定金\N{\fs12}Well, I just... put down a deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.49,0:35:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,- 尼克  - 不  只是\N{\fs12}- Nick... - No. It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.03,0:36:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有很多问题要考虑  那样不太安全\N{\fs12}you know, there's so much... that's just not safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.78,0:36:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而且你知道的  很多事都不太行\N{\fs12}and, uh... you know, so much that doesn't work and...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.53,0:36:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是  但是  尼克\N{\fs12}Yeah, but, Nick...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.84,0:36:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我想让你住到一个安全的地方\N{\fs12}I want to know that you live somewhere good.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.37,0:36:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,一个安全的地方\N{\fs12}Somewhere... safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.65,0:36:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,你和孩子\N{\fs12}Both you and the baby.
