Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.22,0:36:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们应该把心思放在一些小事上面\N{\fs12}for now we should probably just work on the little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.14,0:36:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小事\N{\fs12}The little things?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.93,0:36:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\fs12}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.65,0:36:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小事\N{\fs12}The little things.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.86,0:37:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,亲爱的\N{\fs12}Honey...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.08,0:37:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的  亲爱的\N{\fs12}everything's gonna work out just fine, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.97,0:37:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们找了最专业的人来帮你\N{\fs12}They got the best people to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.53,0:37:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都会好起来的\N{\fs12}Everything's gonna be just fine.
