Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.11,0:38:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- 准备好了吗  - 好了\N{\fs12}- Ready? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.44,0:38:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs12}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.11,0:39:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,她还好吗\N{\fs12}How is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.58,0:39:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,在睡觉\N{\fs12}Sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.12,0:39:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,她有没有把知道的都告诉警察\N{\fs12}Did she tell the police everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.95,0:39:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,都说了\N{\fs12}Oh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.30,0:39:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道吗  如果我是罗伊  我也会这么做的\N{\fs12}You know, if I were Roy... I would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.43,0:39:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我先到了那里  我也会做同样的事\N{\fs12}lf I'd gotten over there first, I'd have done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.16,0:40:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,她  呃\N{\fs12}She, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.61,0:40:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她不想让我收养她了\N{\fs12}she doesn't want me to adopt her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.72,0:40:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs12}Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.60,0:40:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,她很担心罗伊  说她自己不属于这里\N{\fs12}She's worried about Roy, and she says she doesn't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.87,0:40:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,也许她说得对\N{\fs12}Maybe she's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.00,0:40:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是我太着急想成为\N{\fs12}Maybe I... just tried too damn hard to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.61,0:40:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那个不是自己的自己了\N{\fs12}be something that I really am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.48,0:40:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你做的这些\N{\fs12}What you did, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.99,0:40:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你做的这一切\N{\fs12}Thank you for what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.64,0:40:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,爸  我没做什么事\N{\fs12}Dad, I... I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.21,0:40:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好男人  尼古拉斯\N{\fs12}You're a good man, Nicholas.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.30,0:41:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安\N{\fs12}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.07,0:41:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用在这里陪着我\N{\fs12}You don't have to stay here on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.90,0:41:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我没事的\N{\fs12}I'll be all right.
